4300.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4300.description: SpongeBob and Patrick make a bet to see who can hold a "funny face" the longest...then their faces freeze that way! // SpongeBob and Patrick spend one last glorious - and dangerous - day at Glove World before it closes for good.

4301.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4301.description: A professor leads the kids to a spirit library in the middle of the desert, where Sokka hopes to discover powerful secrets to use against the Fire Nation.

4302.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4302.description: Aang searches for Appa, while Katara struggles to keep everyone together so they can survive in the vast desert. Meanwhile, Uncle and Zuko seek help from an ancient secret society.

4303.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4303.description: There's a new Viking-themed promotion at the Krusty Krab, so SpongeBob is determined to find out everything there is to know about Vikings. And what better way to find out about Vikings than to talk to them himself? // Mermaidman and Barnacleboy are having a book signing, but SpongeBob can't go because he has boating school. After some convincing, Patrick finally gets SpongeBob to take a bathroom break from class.

4304.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4304.description: Mr. Krabs' granddad is coming to town! But instead of being excited, Mr. Krabs is nervous because his swarthy pirate granddad thinks that Mr. Krabs is a pirate, too. // When SpongeBob finds out that Squidward is a member of a secret society, SpongeBob decides he wants to join, too! The only problem is that the society is just for fish with tentacles.

4305.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4305.description: As the Turtles search for Karai, they have to deal with a city filled with Kraangdroids as well as Zeck and Steranko, who hunt Karai for their own means.

4306.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4306.description: Donnie finishes a new batch of retro-mutagen, hoping to save Karai, but the Turtles find themselves hunted by Shredder's new vengeful henchmen. Bebop and Rocksteady!

4307.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4307.description: To impress his fan club, Po releases the Mongolian Fist Demon. Now he has to figure out how to defeat the Demon and save the village and his fans!

4308.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4308.description: Po disobeys Shifu's orders and looks into the Mystical Mirror of Yin and Yang, creating two versions of himself: one good and one evil!

4309.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4309.description: Best Laid Plaintains: It’s a special day when Bada and Bing get a shipment of delicious plantains to eat. Although they jealously guard the African bananas, King Julien’s determined to taste them too. He sneaks into the gorilla habitat while they sleep, and he and Marlene end up eating a few too many for the gorillas not to notice. Like all of them. When they realize what they’ve done they head for the hills as fast as their stolen car can take them. Can the penguins calm the savage beasts before they bash the banana bandits? P.E.L.T.: Skipper’s losing it. His performance on the obstacle course is actually slowing down, so he has to trigger a special fitness test to prove he can still lead the squad. Kowalski takes over as Skipper excuses himself to go on his fitness quest. The brainy bird appears to do a bang-up job in the leadership role – are Skipper’s days at the helm over but he’s too chicken to admit it?

4310.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4310.description: The Space Agency intends to send one of the chimps to the moon. In the opinion of certain flightless waterfowl, this important mission would be much better served by sending a flightless waterfowl instead. Private proves to be best suited for the trip (believe it or not) and with the help of a clever monkey suit disguise, he ends up on the moon.

4311.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4311.description: In the battle for fast food supremacy, Plankton has decided to throw in the towel and start a new business selling trinkets and souvenir gifts. He even renames his store from The Chum Bucket to The Chumporium. // Gary starts biting everyone in town, starting with Squidward. When Squid asks if Gary has been up-to-date on all of his snail shots, SpongeBob reveals that he's never done any of that before.

4312.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4312.description: Mr. Krabs is about to be fined for unfair labor practices. It turns out that in all the years he has been working at the Krusty Krab, SpongeBob has never taken a vacation. // SpongeBob finds an old powdered wig in the trash and wears it around town thinking it is the height of all things cool. The townspeople laugh at him, and Mr. Krabs makes him wear a ridiculous hairnet.

4313.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4313.description: When Squidward swallows his clarinet reed Sandy offers to retrieve the piece by shrinking herself and a mini sub down to microscopic proportions and traveling into Squid's body. // A misunderstanding over a vacation getaway advertisement causes Patrick to think he must "get out of town" or face dire consequences.

4314.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4314.description: When Nella invites a group of Chomplings to sleep over in the Clubhouse, they cramp Blaine's style. Until he realizes the real reason they need a home. // Nella must rescue Blaine when his tall tales become an unexpected reality.

4315.title: Nella The Princess Knight
4315.description: Riley secretly enlists the help of a music loving dragon to play a duet with Nella in her big recital. // Dwayne is nervous about going on his first quest as Blaine's steed.

4316.title: Bubble Guppies
4316.description: Rawrrrrrr! While the Bubble Guppies are digging for dinosaur bones, they learn all about different types of dinosaurs.

4317.title: Bubble Guppies
4317.description: To celebrate Shrimptennial, the Bubble Guppies visit Big Bubble City! Join them in discovering the hustle and bustle of the big city and the Big Bubble Building!

4318.title: Dora the Explorer
4318.description: Boots is thrilled to hear about the riddle contest today at the Tall Mountain. Who can solve the silliest riddle?

4319.title: Dora the Explorer
4319.description: Uh oh! A Big Storm Cloud is coming. Dora and Boots have to warn all their friends in the forest to get home fast so the Big Storm Cloud doesn't rain on them and get them wet.

4320.title: Rusty Rivets
4320.description: When the Bits find a satellite crashed in the scrapyard, Rusty has to find a way to get the satellite bit back home to space! // Rusty and the gang must move a sick fish to the Nature Park for treatment.

4321.title: Rusty Rivets
4321.description: When Mr. Higgins accidentally fills a GIANT beach ball with water instead of air, it's up to the gang to get it to the lake without popping so it doesn't flood the town. // Rusty and Ruby get stranded on an island when they compete to see who can pick up the most garbage at the lake.

4322.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
4322.description: When Crusher tries to cheat at a carnival game, he accidentally strands himself and Pickle on a giant rocket! Now it’s up to Blaze and AJ to rescue the two trucks before their runaway rocket crashes into the garbage dump.

4323.title: Blaze And The Monster Machines
4323.description: Gabby, Blaze and AJ are out in the wilderness when they get a call, Blaze's friends have come down with a sickness called the Sneezles! Our heroes must race back to Axle City to bring the sick trucks the medicine oil they need.

4324.title: PAW Patrol
4324.description: Mr. Porters van full of puppy food slides on the ice near the shore; Ryder and the PAW Patrol must save the day! // Katie and her cat Cali are on the chair lift when it stops leaving them above the ski hill with no way to get down!

4325.title: PAW Patrol
4325.description: We see a flashback of how Rubble became a member of the Paw Patrol! // When Wally the Walrus gets tangled in an old fishing net, Ryder and the Paw Patrol need to get him to the surface and back to shore safely.

4326.title: PAW Patrol
4326.description: Farmer Yumi's carrots are disappearing and she calls Ryder and the Paw Patrol for help. // Katie is excited to be entering one of the Paw Patrol pups into a puppy grooming competition "Puptacular" in the next town.

4327.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4327.description: SpongeBob eats some sea onion ice cream and his breath stinks. When people avoid him, Pat convinces SpongeBob that it's because he's ugly. // When Mr. Krabs gives his daughter Pearl a job at the Krusty krab, she starts to make some big changes in the menu and atmosphere. SpongeBob is threatened and doesn't like the new "management" but after a bit he gets used to it.

4328.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4328.description: Pat feels like he hasn't accomplished anything with his life and he decides to take SpongeBob on as his role model. At first, SpongeBob is flattered, but soon Pat takes the idea too far and begins to take over SpongeBob's life. // Pat's out of town and Spongebob is feeling lonely one day so he blows a bubble to keep him company. As he walks around town talking to his friend , everyone thinks he's taking this imaginary friend thing too far and needs help.

4329.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4329.description: When Squidward accidentally lets SpongeBob eat an exploding pie, he feels guilty and resolves to make SpongeBob's few remaining hours left in the world enjoyable. // Plankton schemes to steal the Krabby patty by disguising himself as Mr. Krabs and infiltrating the Krusty Krab.

4330.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4330.description: Private discovers a stack of lost comic books. Skipper immediately commands their destruction, citing their risky influence. // Shakespeare in the park has inspired Private as he struts around the zoo spouting iambic pentameter laden insults.

4331.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4331.description: The penguins have had enough of the crazy lemurs 24 hour parting! They hack into the zoo habitat schematic and successfully transfer the lemurs to the petting zoo. // The penguins journey to the bottom of the Atlantic for 100 year-old preserved herring.

4332.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4332.description: After dealing Taotie yet another humiliating defeat, Po is horrified to learn that the villainous warthog has had a full on nervous breakdown. Po is determined to heal his spirit and Taotie is eager to change his evil ways...or is he?

4333.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4333.description: When Po's fake love letter prank on Monkey backfires, the duo's relationship is put to the test in a story of jealousy, betrayal and, yes, even kidnapping.

4334.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4334.description: Mikey and Casey are befriended by Mondo Gecko, a radical skateboarding reptilian kid.

4335.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4335.description: Karai is brainwashed and starts hunting the Turtles.

4336.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4336.description: After receiving an invitation to a gallery opening, Squidward scrambles to find a friend to take with him. // While trying to order a special sandwich, Patrick gets swept up in the fast paced world of business.

4337.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4337.description: When SpongeBob cooks at home, Mr. Krabs' customers leave his restaurant and head for SpongeBob's Place. // When Plankton gets kicked out of the house, it's up to SpongeBob to teach him how to win his computer wife back.

4338.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4338.description: When stray snails start appearing around Bikini Bottom, SpongeBob decides to care for them himself. // To defend Bikini Bottom’s honor, Patrick enters a Krabby Patty eating competition.

4339.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4339.description: When Temutai kidnaps a kung fu master, Shifu turns to Po for help.

4340.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4340.description: Po discovers his dad, Mr. Ping, is dating Scorpion, but he has trouble trusting his former enemy who claims to no longer be evil.

4341.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4341.description: When a sneeze from Rico causes the underground tunnel system beneath the zoo to rupture Skipper calls in 4 beavers to fix the situation. // Skipper's having one of those perfect days, and he decides to use the opportunity to settle an old score.

4342.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4342.description: When Doris the Dolphin shows up with Parker the Platypus and asks a favor of Kowalski, he instantly jumps to her rescue only to find out it’s to free her brother Francis who happens to be a “mind-jacked” Dr. Blowhole.

4343.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4343.description: Leo doesn't trust Slash when he emerges leading a team called the "Mighty Mutanimals".

4344.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4344.description: While the Mighty Mutanimals lay siege to TCRI, the Turtles must brave the bizarre world of Dimension X to save the enslaved people of New York.

4345.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4345.description: SpongeBob learns that "imitation is the sincerest form of flattery" - too bad no one told him how to stop! // When worms move in to SpongeBob's holes, it's up to him to hide his disgusting new friends from everyone else.

4346.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4346.description: SpongeBob brings home a box of new snail treats that Gary will do anything to get - especially when they run out. // Plankton wins a free Krabby Patty, and Mr. Krabs will do anything to stop him from collecting.

4347.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4347.description: Plankton teams up with Man Ray to take over the Krusty Krab and then-the world! Hahahahahaha! // Squidward quits the Krusty Krab to work for Plankton, turning the Chum Bucket into an overnight success.

4348.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4348.description: Po realizes he must select a trophy for the Hall of Heroes, but instead finds himself helping a young villager retrieve a rabbit doll that is much more important than it looks.

4349.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4349.description: Po disguises himself as the merciless villain, Tong Fo, to try and locate a hidden weapon.

4350.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4350.description: Rico’s beloved doll, Miss Perky, has a new line of princess accessories! Joy! But in order for Skipper to reward the loco penguin with the new swag he must fill a marble jar (one marble in for good behavior, one marble out for bad.) How in the world is Rico supposed to behave and fill the jar when King Julien has kidnapped his dolly with the intention of marrying her?

4351.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4351.description: When the Penguins lose access to their favorite snack, popcorn, Skipper and crew leap into action to gain a new supply of the salty treat. // When a camera falls from the sky into the lemur habitat, Julien and Maurice argue about who will keep the shiny toy. But when Maurice disappears in the struggle, the Penguins are called in to find the missing lemur.

4352.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4352.description: Sokka reviews the maps they acquired from the Spirit Library. After accidentally soaking the maps with a Waterbending bomb (similar to doing a cannonball in a pool), Katara uses her Waterbending to extract the water from the maps. The group then huddles around the map to discuss in which direction they should go – the Serpent's Pass appears to be the most direct route.

4353.title: Avatar: The Last Airbender
4353.description: Aang discovers a secret Fire Nation super weapon heading straight for Ba Sing Se and must stop it before it destroys the great wall that protects the city from invasion. Meanwhile, Jet wishes to recruit Zuko for his Freedom Fighters, but learns a dangerous secret about him instead.

4354.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4354.description: The Good Krabby Name: Mr. Krabs wants all of Bikini Bottom to eat at the Krusty Krab, so SpongeBob and Patrick go on an advertising blitz. Move It or Lose It: Mr. Krabs and Plankton circulate petitions to see which restaurant will get bulldozed by the city.

4355.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4355.description: SpongeBob and Patrick try to join the extreme sports team The Drasticals. // Sandy finds a book of world’s records, and tries to break them all with SpongeBob’s help.

4356.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4356.description: SpongeBob learns his milkshake license has expired, and is forced to go back to the milkshake academy. // Squidward hits his head and reverts to being a baby, and it's up to SpongeBob and Patrick to take care of him.

4357.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4357.description: Casey Jones thinks he can take on the criminal underworld on his own, but he soon finds himself in over his head.

4358.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles
4358.description: A new mutant called Muckman starts to gain notoriety as NYC's "Monster Hero".

4359.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4359.description: When Taotie tries to destroy the Jade Palace and fails, he is sent to prison while his son, Bian Zao, is left behind with Po, who acts like a big brother to the boy who thinks everything is lame!

4360.title: Kung Fu Panda: Legends of Awesomeness
4360.description: While repairs are being made to the noodle shop, Mr. Ping turns the training hall into a restaurant!

4361.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4361.description: When the zoo installs web cams to bring in new visitors, Private accidentally becomes an Internet star. // Skipper accidentally causes King Julien to lose his beloved crown. The penguins go on a dangerous mission to retrieve the crown from the sewer.

4362.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4362.description: Sick of Julien's annoying presence, the penguins decide to take a vacation on The Moon. // After Marlene is frightened by a spooky noise in the night, she and Skipper travel down to the sewer below the zoo to find the source of the scary moans.

4363.title: The Penguins of Madagascar
4363.description: When stuffed Mort dolls become popular at the zoo, Julien gets jealous and get them recalled. Unfortunately, the real-life Mort is accidentally sent back to the factory along with his plush replicas. // Maurice bribes the zoo animals to celebrate “King Julien Day” by offering them candy. Only Skipper refuses to go along, but still he’s unable to avoid the annoying day.

4364.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4364.description: Squidward finds SpongeBob's diary, and starts reading it out loud in the Krusty Krab. // SpongeBob once again fails his driving test, forcing Mrs. Puff to think outside the box--and off the road.

4365.title: SpongeBob SquarePants
4365.description: An imprisoned Plankton teams up with his fellow inmates to break out of jail and steal the Krabby Patty secret formula. // SpongeBob replaces his broken spatula with one from Plankton, which may or may not have magical powers.
